<h2>Workers of the world unite!</h2>

<p>You have nothing to lose but your chains.</p>
<p>Thus we shall never experience our relationship to the essence of technology so long as we merely conceive and push forward the technological, put up with it, or evade it. Everywhere we remain unfree and chained to technology, whether we passionately affirm or deny it.</p>

